      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WEINKARTE ═══ -->
  <section class="weinkarte" id="weinkarte">
    <div class="weinkarte-header">
      <div class="section-label">Unsere Empfehlungen</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Was wir gerade lieben</h2>
      <p class="weinkarte-subtitle">
        Drei Weine, die uns diese Saison nicht loslassen.
        Handverlesen von unserer Sommeliere Marie.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="wine-grid">
      <!-- Wine 1 -->
      <div class="wine-card">
        <div class="wine-card-number">01</div>
        <div class="wine-card-region">Mosel, Deutschland</div>
        <h3 class="wine-card-name">Schieferberg Riesling Kabinett 2022</h3>
        <div class="wine-card-grape">Riesling</div>
        <div class="wine-card-divider"></div>
        <p class="wine-card-note">
          Schiefer und Zitrusbluete, dann ein Hauch Pfirsich,
          der minutenlang nachklingt. Leichtfuessig und dabei unendlich tief.
        </p>
        <div class="wine-card-price">
          <div class="wine-card-price-glass">
            Glas
            <span>8,50 &euro;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="wine-card-price-bottle">
            Flasche
            <span>34 &euro;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wine 2 -->
      <div class="wine-card">
        <div class="wine-card-number">02</div>
        <div class="wine-card-region">Bordeaux, Frankreich</div>
        <h3 class="wine-card-name">Chateau Beaumont 2019</h3>
        <div class="wine-card-grape">Cabernet Sauvignon, Merlot</div>
        <div class="wine-card-divider"></div>
        <p class="wine-card-note">
          Dunkle Kirschen, Tabak, ein lederner Unterton.
          Ein Wein, der sich anfuehlt wie ein langer Abend
          am Kamin — warm, ruhig, vollkommen.
        </p>
        <div class="wine-card-price">
          <div class="wine-card-price-glass">
            Glas
            <span>11 &euro;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="wine-card-price-bottle">
            Flasche
            <span>46 &euro;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wine 3 -->
      <div class="wine-card">
        <div class="wine-card-number">03</div>
        <div class="wine-card-region">Toskana, Italien</div>
        <h3 class="wine-card-name">Tenuta di Trinoro 2020</h3>
        <div class="wine-card-grape">Cabernet Franc, Merlot, Petit Verdot</div>
        <div class="wine-card-divider"></div>
        <p class="wine-card-note">
          Opulent und wild zugleich. Brombeere, schwarzer Pfeffer,
          mediterranes Gestruepp nach dem Regen. Fuer besondere Abende.
        </p>
        <div class="wine-card-price">
          <div class="wine-card-price-glass">
            Glas
            <span>18 &euro;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="wine-card-price-bottle">
            Flasche
            <span>89 &euro;</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
